"from\": 686, \"to\": 693}, {\"ngram\": \"negative publicity\", \"from\": 697, \"to\": 715}, {\"ngram\": \"the sporting mega\", \"from\": 720, \"to\": 737}, {\"ngram\": \"event\", \"from\": 738, \"to\": 743}, {\"ngram\": \"just six months\", \"from\": 764, \"to\": 779}, {\"ngram\": \"a television audience\", \"from\": 789, \"to\": 810}, {\"ngram\": \"billions\", \"from\": 814, \"to\": 822}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many Parisians were dismayed in December by news that transport ticket prices are set to double for the duration of the event and that they should work from home to free up seats on busy metros and buses.\", \"from\": 825, \"to\": 1029, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Many Parisians\", \"from\": 825, \"to\": 839}, {\"ngram\": \"December\", \"from\": 857, \"to\": 865}, {\"ngram\": \"news\", \"from\": 869, \"to\": 873}, {\"ngram\": \"transport ticket prices\", \"from\": 879, \"to\": 902}, {\"ngram\": \"the duration\", \"from\": 925, \"to\": 937}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 941, \"to\": 950}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 982, \"to\": 986}, {\"ngram\": \"seats\", \"from\": 998, \"to\": 1003}, {\"ngram\": \"busy metros\", \"from\": 1007, \"to\": 1018}, {\"ngram\": \"buses\", \"from\": 1023, \"to\": 1028}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The unveiling of planned security measures led to claims some parts of the city would face Covid-19-style lockdowns, while controversy erupted about the environmental impact of a judges' tower at the surfing venue in French Polynesia.\", \"from\": 1031, \"to\": 1265, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1255, \"end\": 1264, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\", \"score\": 0.9848748267072021, \"rank\": 0.015357454636188768, \"text\": \"Polynesia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The unveiling\", \"from\": 1031, \"to\": 1044}, {\"ngram\": \"planned security measures\", \"from\": 1048,